{
  "stem": "5188.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 21.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Now, we were supposed to leave for New York in the middle or the end of January.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It must have been the end of January, sure, because the-- we booked passage on the United States Lines.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "My father was so wise that he did that because he wanted to be out of Germany as soon as he saw himself, you know, able to do that.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So once we were on the boat, we were going to be in United States territory, even though the boat was going to leave from Hamburg.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The United States Lines steamers at the time went from Hamburg to Le Havre and then to Cobh, which I believe is in England, and then on to New York.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They made these stops.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we were scheduled to leave at the end of January to arrive in New York on February 17.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We had booked passage on that liner.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And in the meantime, my father was going to visit the relatives and, you know, and do things.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But we had to be at the house at the beginning-- before January 1st, because the new owners were going to take over.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So I went to stay with the relatives in Rheinbach.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Ketchen and Fritz were in Rheinbach.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I loved those relatives, because that was also where my cousin Fritz, who was our apprentice, lived-- that's his parents-- and his older brother, Otto.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I got along so well with those boys.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They were my favorite cousins.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I loved being with them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I would trail after them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They were about five, six, seven years older than I was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I was a little girl.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They thought I was a little toy to play with, so they liked me and I liked them.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
